the enclosed file COPYING for license information (GPL). If you
did not receive this file, see https://www.gnu.org/licenses/gpl-3.0.txt.

*
         * @prop {String|undefined} label
         * @description
         *   Label linked to the form field.

*
         * @prop {Array|undefined} labelPlaceholder
         * @description
         *   The label placeholder values for the replacement during the translation of the current label.

*
         * @prop {Boolean|undefined} labelSrOnly
         * @default false
         * @description
         *   Controls whether the label will be shown only to screen readers, thus being invisible on page.

*
         * @prop {String|undefined} placeholder
         * @description
         *   Text inside the field to help the user.

*
         * @prop {String|undefined} description
         * @description
         *   Help text used to describe the purpose of the field.

*
         * @prop {Boolean|undefined} hideDescription
         * @default false
         * @description
         *   Hides field description under an info hover icon showed next to the label.

*
         * @prop {String|undefined} error
         * @description
         *   Validation error message to display.

*
         * @prop {Boolean|undefined} required
         * @default false
         * @description
         *   Whether the field should be marked as required (mandatory).

*
         * @prop {String|undefined} name
         * @description
         *   Value of the name attribute of the form field.

*
         * @prop {Boolean|undefined} disabled
         * @default false
         * @description
         *   Whether or not the field is disabled.

*
         * @prop {Boolean|undefined} hidden
         * @default false
         * @description
         *   Whether or not the field is hidden.

*
         * @prop {Boolean|undefined} readonly
         * @default false
         * @description
         *   Whether the field should be read only.

*
             * @event loaded
             * @description
             *   Raised when the form field component has been loaded and is ready for usage.
